Options +FollowSymLinks
Options -Indexes
RewriteEngine On

DirectoryIndex index.php

RewriteRule ^([a-z]+)/([A-Za-z0-9]+)$ ./index.php?controller=$1&action=$2&%{QUERY_STRING}
RewriteRule ^([a-z]+)/([A-Za-z0-9]+)/$ ./index.php?controller=$1&action=$2&%{QUERY_STRING}
RewriteRule ^([a-z]+)/?$ ./index.php?controller=$1&%{QUERY_STRING}